The paper proposes a method for improving exploration in deep reinforcement learning, which is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method is evaluated on robotic tasks, which suggests that it could also fall under the sub-categories of robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper uses visual inputs for some of the tasks, which could also place it under the sub-category of computer vision (cs.CV).
